<br>
    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">There are three steps you have to follow to use this deck correctly. First, always try to play your sites first, since they offer the Uruks an occasional bonus. The second step is to save both Bill Ferny cards until the last few sites so you can use them with a few Uruks to kill Frodo. The last step is to use as many wizard storms as possible after the last santuary so it will be easy to wipe out an entire fellowship. Besides that, just use your Uruks wisely and focus on surviving long enough for your enemy to die from your minions. Just be careful never to let them get a fellowship of four or more, because some good Uruk minions need a lot of twilight. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
